Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
